# Force ML-DSA-87 PKCS#8 DER private keys to be treated as binary.
# Without this, core.autocrlf=true on Windows checkouts can rewrite
# 0x0A bytes to 0x0D 0x0A inside the DER blobs, silently corrupting
# them. The conformance fixture generator relies on these blobs being
# byte-identical across checkouts to produce byte-reproducible
# fixtures (Q-CONF-FIXTURE-GENERATOR-DETERMINISM-01).
*.der binary
